stnAtmVpn.name: stnAtmVpn
stnAtmVpn.contactinfo: Spring Tide Networks, Inc. Customer Service Postal: 3 Clock Tower Place Suite 200 Maynard, MA 01754 USA Tel: +1 978 298 2000 Email: custserv@springtidenet.com
stnAtmVpn.description: This MIB module describes managed objects of Spring Tide Networks ATM VPN Interfaces.

stnAtmVpnTrunkTable.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkTable
stnAtmVpnTrunkTable.description: A list of ATM VPN Trunk entries.

stnAtmVpnTrunkEntry.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkEntry
stnAtmVpnTrunkEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular ATM VPN Trunk.

stnAtmVpnTrunkIfIndex.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkIfIndex
stnAtmVpnTrunkIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the ATM VPN Trunk Interface.

stnAtmVpnTrunkViId.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkViId
stnAtmVpnTrunkViId.description: The instance of the configuration record corresponding to this ATM VPN Trunk.

stnAtmVpnTrunkName.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkName
stnAtmVpnTrunkName.description: The name configured for this ATM VPN Trunk.

stnAtmVpnTrunkState.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkState
stnAtmVpnTrunkState.description: The current operational state of the ATM VPN Trunk.

stnAtmVpnTrunkLowerIfIndex.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkLowerIfIndex
stnAtmVpnTrunkLowerIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the Interface below the ATM VPN Trunk Interface.

stnAtmVpnTrunkVpnPaths.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkVpnPaths
stnAtmVpnTrunkVpnPaths.description: The number of VPN Paths that this ATM VPN Trunk has in its forwarding table.

stnAtmVpnTrunkInUnknownVpnId.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkInUnknownVpnId
stnAtmVpnTrunkInUnknownVpnId.description: The number packets received with a Vpn-Id that was not present it the ATM VPN Trunk's forwarding table.

stnAtmVpnTrunkInVpnIdIfaceInvalid.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkInVpnIdIfaceInvalid
stnAtmVpnTrunkInVpnIdIfaceInvalid.description: The number packets received with a Vpn-Id that was known, but the entry in the FIB refered to an invalid or non-existant interface. This can indicate an invalid configuration.

stnAtmVpnTrunkOutUnknownVpnId.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkOutUnknownVpnId
stnAtmVpnTrunkOutUnknownVpnId.description: The number packets passed to this trunk from another ATM VPN Trunk or Link with a Vpn-Id that was not present it the ATM VPN Trunk's forwarding table.

stnAtmVpnTrunkOutVpnIdIfaceInvalid.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkOutVpnIdIfaceInvalid
stnAtmVpnTrunkOutVpnIdIfaceInvalid.description: The number packets passed to this trunk from another ATM VPN Trunk or Link when there was no suitable interface below the ATM VPN Trunk.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathTable.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathTable
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathTable.description: A list of the ATM VPN Paths known to a ATM VPN Trunk.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathEntry.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathEntry
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular remote MAC learned on a VEI VcLink.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathTrunkIfIndex.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathTrunkIfIndex
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathTrunkIfIndex.description: The IfIndex of the ATM VPN Trunk Interface which owns the VPN Path entry.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnOUI.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnOUI
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnOUI.description: The VPN OUI for which packets this VPN Path pertains to.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnIndex.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnIndex
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnIndex.description: The VPN Index for which packets this VPN Path pertains to.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnSubIndex.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnSubIndex
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathVpnSubIndex.description: The VPN SubIndex for which packets this VPN Path pertains to.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathType.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathType
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathType.description: Indicates the type of the VPN Path database entry. Learned indicates that the entry was dynamically learned from link/trunk configuration or other dynamic means. Static indicates that the entry was configured explicitly using a VirtualInterfaceInfo Entry.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathNextIfType.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathNextIfType
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathNextIfType.description: Indicates the type of ATM VPN Interface that this path points to.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathNextIfIndex.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathNextIfIndex
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathNextIfIndex.description: The IfIndex of the destination ATM VPN Interface which this path entry refers to.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathInPackets.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathInPackets
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathInPackets.description: The number of packets that have been received by the ATM VPN Trunk for this VPN path.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathInOctets.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathInOctets
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathInOctets.description: The number of octets that have been received by the ATM VPN Trunk for this VPN path.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathOutPackets.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathOutPackets
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathOutPackets.description: The number of packets that have been transmitted by the ATM VPN Trunk for this VPN path.

stnAtmVpnTrunkPathOutOctets.name: stnAtmVpnTrunkPathOutOctets
stnAtmVpnTrunkPathOutOctets.description: The number of octets that have been transmitted by the ATM VPN Trunk for this VPN path.

stnAtmVpnLinkTable.name: stnAtmVpnLinkTable
stnAtmVpnLinkTable.description: A list of ATM VPN Link entries.

stnAtmVpnLinkEntry.name: stnAtmVpnLinkEntry
stnAtmVpnLinkEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkIfIndex.name: stnAtmVpnLinkIfIndex
stnAtmVpnLinkIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the ATM VPN Link Interface.

stnAtmVpnLinkViId.name: stnAtmVpnLinkViId
stnAtmVpnLinkViId.description: The instance of the configuration record corresponding to this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkName.name: stnAtmVpnLinkName
stnAtmVpnLinkName.description: The name configured for this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkVpnOUI.name: stnAtmVpnLinkVpnOUI
stnAtmVpnLinkVpnOUI.description: The Vpn OUI that is associated with this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkVpnIndex.name: stnAtmVpnLinkVpnIndex
stnAtmVpnLinkVpnIndex.description: The Vpn Index that is associated with this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkVpnSubIndex.name: stnAtmVpnLinkVpnSubIndex
stnAtmVpnLinkVpnSubIndex.description: The Vpn SubIndex that is associated with this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkState.name: stnAtmVpnLinkState
stnAtmVpnLinkState.description: The current operational state of the ATM VPN LINK.

stnAtmVpnLinkTrunkViId.name: stnAtmVpnLinkTrunkViId
stnAtmVpnLinkTrunkViId.description: The instance of the configuration record corresponding to the ATM VPN Trunk associated with this ATM VPN Link. If the value is zero, then no ATM VPN Trunk is currently associated with this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkLowerIfIndex.name: stnAtmVpnLinkLowerIfIndex
stnAtmVpnLinkLowerIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the Interface below the ATM VPN Link Interface.

stnAtmVpnLinkOutUnknownVpnId.name: stnAtmVpnLinkOutUnknownVpnId
stnAtmVpnLinkOutUnknownVpnId.description: The number packets passed from an ATM VPN Trunk with a Vpn-Id that was appropriate for the ATM VPN Link's forwarding table.

stnAtmVpnLinkOutVpnIdIfaceInvalid.name: stnAtmVpnLinkOutVpnIdIfaceInvalid
stnAtmVpnLinkOutVpnIdIfaceInvalid.description: The number packets passed from an ATM VPN Trunk when no appropriate interface exists below this ATM VPN Link.

stnAtmVpnLinkInVpnIdIfaceInvalid.name: stnAtmVpnLinkInVpnIdIfaceInvalid
stnAtmVpnLinkInVpnIdIfaceInvalid.description: The number packets received when there was no appropriate ATM VPN Trunk Interface present.
